    "2026-04: Filled Lander/Gunboat/BlackBoat for Mech/Recon/Tank/MedTank/NeoTank/MegaTank (AWBW ground-vs-transport; cross-check https://awbw.fandom.com/wiki/Damage_Chart \u2014 automated fetch may hit Cloudflare). Was null, which hid legal adjacent fire in get_attack_targets and oracle Fire (no path).",
    "2026-04: Tank vs B-Copter / T-Copter set to 55 / 85 (MG vs light air per AWBW; confirm at https://awbw.fandom.com/wiki/Damage_Chart). Was null; GL replay 1624764 records Tank vs B-Copter adjacent direct fire (PHP snapshot + combatInfo), which get_attack_targets must allow.",
    "2026-04: MedTank/NeoTank/MegaTank vs BCopter/TCopter set to 35/35 (MG). Was null; GL lane A 1621898 / 1629921 (Neo vs B-Copter). Recon/Infantry/Mech unchanged here; awbw.fandom.com/wiki/Damage_Chart returned 404 when authored \u2014 values taken from AWBW replay combat envelopes for those games.",
    "2026-04 (agent4): Infantry/Mech vs B-Copter/T-Copter filled with AW2 canon (Inf 7/3, Mech MG 9/5) per awbw.fandom.com/wiki/Damage_Chart; previously null hid the strike entirely (engine refused legitimate foot-vs-rotor fire \u2014 e.g. GL 1635708 P0 Inf vs P1 T-Copter). Foot vs Fighter/Bomber/Stealth left null: per AW2/AWBW, ground MGs cannot target fixed-wing; null is the documented \"cannot target\" sentinel here.",
    "2026-04: Tank vs Battleship set to 15 (AWBW amarriner damage.php row; adjacent shore direct fire). Was null; GL 1630784 records Tank vs Battleship Fire (no path), which get_attack_targets must allow.",
    "2026-04: MedTank/NeoTank/MegaTank vs Battleship set to 40/55/75 (AW2 direct-fire chart; Tank vs BB already 15). Was null; GL 1631194 Neo vs adjacent Battleship Fire (no path) required get_base_damage non-null.",
    "2026-04: B-Copter vs Battleship set to 25 (AW2 primary missiles vs naval; GameFAQs AW2 damage guide / Fandom Battle Helicopter matchups). Was null; GL extras 1630781 day 21 second adjacent B-Copter vs Battleship Fire (no path) required get_attack_targets / oracle resolver non-null."
